flowchart TD
  START([evaluate name + context]) --> READ[read definition from provider]
  READ -->|not found| NF[FeatureRejected\nthrow FeatureNotFoundError]
  READ --> CK{cache hit?\nkey = ns:name:checksum:ctxHash}
  CK -->|yes| HIT[return cached result\nrecord cacheHit]
  CK -->|no| INT{checksum valid?}
  INT -->|no| IErr[record integrityFailure\nFeatureRejected\nthrow IntegrityError]
  INT -->|yes| STATE{state}

  STATE -->|archived| OFF1[off value\nreason = archived]
  STATE -->|disabled| OFF2[off value\nreason = disabled]
  STATE -->|enabled| TGT{targeting constraints\nplatform/version/country/region/tenant/env}

  TGT -->|not matched| OFF3[off value\nreason = not_targeted · failed]
  TGT -->|matched| RULES[ordered rules\npriority desc, then declared order]

  RULES --> RMATCH{rule matches?}
  RMATCH -->|yes + no rollout| RV[rule.value\nreason = rule_match]
  RMATCH -->|yes + rollout included| RV
  RMATCH -->|yes + rollout excluded| RULES
  RMATCH -->|no more rules| FROLL{flag rollout?}

  FROLL -->|included| DIN[default value\nreason = rollout_included]
  FROLL -->|excluded| OFF4[off value\nreason = rollout_excluded]
  FROLL -->|none| DEF[default value\nreason = default]

  OFF1 --> CACHE[cache result · record cacheMiss]
  OFF2 --> CACHE
  OFF3 --> CACHE
  OFF4 --> CACHE
  RV --> CACHE
  DIN --> CACHE
  DEF --> CACHE
  CACHE --> EMIT[emit FeatureEvaluated / FeatureRejected\nrecord evaluation + latency]
  HIT --> EMIT
  EMIT --> END([result: value · reason · served · explanation])
